== 调查與逮捕 ==
案件調查由[[聯邦調查局|聯邦調查局]]主導，並由[[美國菸酒槍炮及爆裂物管理局|菸酒槍炮及爆裂物管理局]]、[[美國緝毒局|緝毒局]]、[[美國國家反恐怖行動中心|國家反恐中心]]和[[中央情報局|中央情報局]]等其他聯邦單位協助，初步定位為[[恐怖攻擊|恐怖攻擊]]。[[塔利班|塔利班]]組織表示並未涉入此次之爆炸案。<ref name="Fox News2">{{cite news|url=http://www.foxnews.com/us/2013/04/15/explosion-reported-near-finish-line-boston-marathon-spokesman-says/#ixzz2QZSeFd5B|title=At least 2 dead, dozens hurt after two bombs explode at Boston Marathon|date=2013-04-15|work=[[Fox_News_Channel|Fox News Channel]]|accessdate=2013-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130416000147/http://www.foxnews.com/us/2013/04/15/explosion-reported-near-finish-line-boston-marathon-spokesman-says/#ixzz2QZSeFd5B|archive-date=2013-04-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="Goldman">{{cite news|url=http://abcnews.go.com/blogs/headlines/2013/04/live-updates-boston-marathon-explosion/|title=LIVE UPDATES: Boston Marathon Explosion – ABC News|last=Goldman|first=Russell|date=2013-04-15|work=ABC News|accessdate=2013-04-15|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125023835/https://abcnews.go.com/blogs/headlines/2013/04/live-updates-boston-marathon-explosion/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
{{Wide image|Boston marathon event map.png|900px|波士頓馬拉松爆炸案 (1) 有關事件圖和嫌犯追捕過程 (大約時間)<br/>2) 4月18日 10:30 pm – MIT校警尚恩·柯利爾 (Sean Collier) 遭槍殺<br/>3) 4月18日 11:00 pm – 運動休旅車 (SUV) 遭劫持<br/>4) 4月18日 緊接在後 – 運動休旅車駕駛脫逃，沒有受傷<br/>5) 4月18日 11:18 pm – 自動櫃員機 (ATM) 攝影機照片確認為沙尼耶夫兄弟<br/>6) 4月19日 1:00 am – 警方和嫌犯於水鎮Laurel大道爆發槍戰。[[塔米爾南·沙尼耶夫|塔米爾南·沙尼耶夫]]重傷送醫不治。[[喬卡·沙尼耶夫|喬卡·沙尼耶夫]]脫逃<br/>7) 4月19日 7:00 pm – 水鎮Franklin街爆發更多槍戰。[[喬卡·沙尼耶夫|喬卡·沙尼耶夫]]於一民宅後停放的小船裡被發現，約於8:45 pm 被逮捕。}}

4月18日下午5點20分左右，聯邦調查局公布了波士頓馬拉松賽爆炸案的兩名嫌疑人的照片和錄像。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2013/04/130418_boston_bombing_fbi_suspects.shtml|title=FBI公布了波士頓爆炸案嫌疑人照片|publisher=BBC中文網|date=2013-04-18|accessdate=2013-04-19|archive-date=2013-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130420053734/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2013/04/130418_boston_bombing_fbi_suspects.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>當天晚上，[[麻省理工學院|-{zh-hans:麻省理工学院;zh-hant:麻省理工學院}-]]爆發槍擊案，26岁的麻省理工学院校警尚恩·柯利爾（Sean Collier）身中数枪殉職。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2013/04/19/us/boston-area-violence/index.html|title=Boston police: Marathon bombings suspect 'in custody'|publisher=CNN|date=2013-04-20|accessdate=2013-04-20|archive-date=2020-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208015332/https://edition.cnn.com/2013/04/19/us/boston-area-violence/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

4月19日，美国东部时间凌晨，警方表示[[麻省理工學院|-{zh-hans:麻省理工学院;zh-hant:麻省理工學院}-]]槍擊案嫌疑人也是波士頓馬拉松賽爆炸案嫌疑人，其中一名嫌犯塔米爾南·沙尼耶夫（{{lang|ru|Тамерлан Царнаев}}；{{lang|en|Tamerlan Tsarnaev}}）在追捕期間被擊中，送医院后不治身亡，另一名嫌犯[[麻州大学达特茅斯分校|麻州大学达特茅斯分校]]的学生[[喬卡·沙尼耶夫|喬卡·沙尼耶夫]]（{{lang|ru|Джохар Царнаев}}；{{lang|en|Dzhokhar A. Tsarnaev}}）仍然在逃，3名執法官員證實了此二人為兄弟。其中一人和嫌犯的叔叔確認了塔梅蘭·薩納耶夫的身份。薩納耶夫兄弟居住在波士頓附近，已在美國生活了10年，而兄弟二人均來自[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]][[車臣共和國|車臣共和國]]附近的一個地區。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2013/04/130419_boston_suspects.shtml|title=波士頓爆炸案一嫌犯被擊斃 一嫌犯在逃|publisher=BBC中文網|date=2013-04-19|accessdate=2013-04-19|archive-date=2013-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130422231459/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2013/04/130419_boston_suspects.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

4月19日，美国东部时间白天，波士顿全城关闭所有公共交通系统，停止运营。大批警力和聯邦調查局进行搜捕嫌犯的行动。

4月19日，美国东部时间晚上10:30左右，警方宣布，在逃嫌犯[[喬卡·沙尼耶夫|喬卡·沙尼耶夫]]在毗邻波士顿的[[水鎮_(麻薩諸塞州)|水鎮]]中彈被捕。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2013/04/19/us/boston-area-violence/index.html|title='CAPTURED!!!' Boston police announce Marathon bombing suspect in custody|publisher=CNN|date=2013-04-20|accessdate=2013-04-20|archive-date=2020-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208015332/https://edition.cnn.com/2013/04/19/us/boston-area-violence/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>嫌犯被捕前藏在一个院子里的小艇裡。他被捕前曾经在一张纸上写下作案的原因是报复美国在伊拉克和阿富汗对穆斯林的打击，称爆炸案的受害者是附带损失，就像美国进行军事行动时造成的平民伤亡一样。<ref>{{cite web|title=Boston bombings suspect Dzhokhar Tsarnaev left note in boat he hid in, sources say|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-505263_162-57584771/boston-bombings-suspect-dzhokhar-tsarnaev-left-note-in-boat-he-hid-in-sources-say/?tag=nl.e879&s_cid=e879&ttag=e879|publisher=CBS News|accessdate=2013-05-16|archive-date=2019-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190911233933/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/boston-bombings-suspect-dzhokhar-tsarnaev-left-note-in-boat-he-hid-in-sources-say/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Suspect: Boston payback for hits on Muslims |url=http://www.cnn.com/2013/05/16/us/boston-bombing-investigation/index.html?hpt=hp_t2 |newspaper=CNN |accessdate=2013-05-16 |archive-date=2017-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170802123757/http://www.cnn.com/2013/05/16/us/boston-bombing-investigation/index.html?hpt=hp_t2 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Bombing suspect left note inside boat |url=http://www.wpri.com/dpp/news/local_news/se_mass/sources-bombing-suspect-left-note-in-boat-he-hid-in |publisher=WPRI TV |accessdate=2013-05-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130522132631/http://www.wpri.com/dpp/news/local_news/se_mass/sources-bombing-suspect-left-note-in-boat-he-hid-in |archivedate=2013-05-22 }}</ref>还在游艇的壁上写下了“Fuck America”。<ref>{{cite news|title='F***' America,' Boston Marathon Bomb Suspect Wrote in Boat: Officials|url=http://abcnews.go.com/Blotter/america-boston-marathon-bomb-suspect-wrote-boat-officials/story?id=19193153#.UZUAEKK1HxB|newspaper=ABC News|accessdate=2013-05-16|archive-date=2020-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712040824/https://abcnews.go.com/Blotter/america-boston-marathon-bomb-suspect-wrote-boat-officials/story?id=19193153#.UZUAEKK1HxB|dead-url=no}}</ref>

據政府官员向CNN转述，喬卡·沙尼耶夫在医院接受讯问時表示，案件是他和兄長二人的單獨行動，主要由塔米爾南·沙尼耶夫推動，喬卡表示塔米爾南想捍衛[[伊斯蘭教|伊斯蘭教]]。<ref>{{Cite news |url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/magazine-22227704 |title = Boston bombings: How to interrogate a suspected terrorist |date = 2013-04-24 |work = BBC News Magazine |accessdate = 2013-04-30 |archive-date = 2018-11-19 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181119063255/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/magazine-22227704 |dead-url = no }}</ref>

